他高校张贴。公开信也在香港杂志刊登，传回中国大陆，外台中文广播报道了这封公开信。 <a href=\"https://t.co/EtrYyg4Co1\">pic.twitter.com/EtrYyg4Co1</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; Shao Jiang 邵江 (@shaojiang) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/shaojiang/status/1081924777974120450?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">January 6, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"und\" dir=\"ltr\"><a href=\"https://t.co/NGEWDhgi1j\">pic.twitter.com/NGEWDhgi1j</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 美国之音中文网 (@VOAChinese) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/VOAChinese/status/1082104283326083073?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">January 7, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">曾经，北大校长去北洋政府保释被捕学生；今天，北大把被捕学生开除。<br />堕落如斯！ <a href=\"https://t.co/8y2mem1Lpj\">pic.twitter.com/8y2mem1Lpj</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 花栗鼠 (@Chipmuck8964) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Chipmuck8964/status/1082159826187149313?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">January 7, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">蔡楚：给在押良心犯寄春节慰问卡<br />38位在押良心犯通讯地址，请补充、转发。<br />陈兵，四川省成都郫县安靖镇正义路3号，成都市看守所，邮编611731<br />王怡，四川省成都新津县新邑至大桥新津县看守所，邮编611430<br />王炳章，广东省韶关市浈江区犁市镇7号信箱6-9，邮编512040<br />补充，曹三强 :云南普洱孟连县看守所? <a href=\"https://t.co/4X5AFDVrmu\">pic.twitter.com/4X5AFDVrmu</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; Cai Chu (@caichu88) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/caichu88/status/1082106598464634880?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">January 7, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">